REFERENCE           11LAC007
LANG_ENGLISH        "Well, it doesn't look like we can just fly her out of here. She's held in place by magnetic moorings and they've got one tough tractor beam online. I can deal with those here, but that doesn't solve the bigger problem. The entrance to the pad is closed and I don't think they're going to just open it for us if we ask politely. You'll have to find the flight control center and open the door to the starpad.  Better get going, I would guess we can expect some company pretty soon. Good luck, Kyle! "
LANG_CHINESE        "嗯，看起来我们没有办法直接驾驶她离开这里。她被磁场固定住了，而且他们还拥有非常强力的牵引光束。我可以在这里解决这些问题，可是我们还有一个更大的问题。通往起降平台的门被关起来了，而且我想就算我们很礼貌的请求他们，他们也不会理我们的。所以你必须找到起降控制中心并且打开通往起降平台的门。你最好开始行动了，我猜很快就会有人来找我们的。祝你好运，凯尔！"

REFERENCE           11LAC008
LANG_ENGLISH        "Well, the bad news is that she's locked down.  The good news is that I can disable the magnetic moorings and a tractor beam from here.  The OTHER bad news is the pad roof; it's closed and I don't think they're going to just open it for us if we ask politely. You'll have to find the flight control center and get access into the starpad where the manual overrides are. Better get going, Kyle! "
LANG_CHINESE        "嗯，坏消息是船被锁住了。好消息是我可以在这里关掉磁场和牵引光束。另外一个更坏的消息是屋顶闸门被关起来了，而且我不认为很礼貌的拜托他们，他们就会开门。你必须找到起降控制中心然后到起降平台去，那里有闸门的手动开关。你最好开始行动了，凯尔！"

