LANG_CHINESE        "他们会逼的迪桑逃走的！"

REFERENCE           12LAC005
LANG_ENGLISH        "Then we'll catch him later.  Getting Desann isn't as important as clearing the city-"
LANG_CHINESE        "那我们以后再抓他就好了。抓到迪桑比不上拯救我们的城市重要--"

REFERENCE           12KJO005
LANG_ENGLISH        "Jan's dead, Lando.  Desann and his minion killed her."
LANG_CHINESE        "简死了，兰多。迪桑和他的爪牙杀了她。"

REFERENCE           12LAC006
LANG_ENGLISH        "...Grife, I'm sorry, Kyle...  Okay,....okay... here's what we'll do.  I'll drop you off on the lower levels.  They've probably been overrun by Remnant troops, so watch out.  Chances are that Desann's operating from one of the loading bays above level ten, but you'll never get in without the proper access codes.  Try to find Carbonite Chamber #17.  I've hidden an old R5 unit there with codes to every loading bay in the city."
LANG_CHINESE        "...天啊，我很抱歉，凯尔...好吧，...好吧...那我们这么办吧。我会在城市的下层放你下来。那边大概到处都是帝国的士兵，所以小心一点。迪桑很有可能在第十层以上的某一个停机坪指挥他们的行动，可是没有正确的通行密码，你是到不了那里的。试试看第17号碳化室。我在那里藏了一个记录着这个城市所有密码的旧R5机器人。"

REFERENCE           12KJO006
LANG_ENGLISH        "You always did plan for the worst..."
LANG_CHINESE        "你真会为最坏的情况做准备..."

REFERENCE           12LAC007
LANG_ENGLISH        "Ever since that run-in with Vader.  Anyway, I'll head up top and gather some old friends from the security force.  We'll work our way down towards your position. If we're lucky, we can trap Desann before the New Republic arrives."
LANG_CHINESE        "自从上次和维达打过交道之后养成的习惯。不管如何，我会回到上层召集一些保安部队的旧朋友。我们朝向你的位置移动。如果幸运的话，我们可以在新共和国部队到达之前抓到迪桑。"

